Constructor:when method having a same as a classname 

->does not have a return type

Types 
1)Default COnstructor -> constructor which does not have a parameter
2)Parameterized Constructor-> which have arguments or parameters
3)Copy Constructor


this keyword ->it will work as a refrence keyword when two variables having a same name in
parameterized constructor





